name: Eventbrite block
descriptionHtml:
Test

async () => {
  const eventId = "112691417062";
  await (0, _reporter.testStep)(
    "Can visit the block editor and add a Eventbrite block",
    async () => {
      const blockId = await blockEditor.insertBlock(
        _eventbrite.default.name(),
        _eventbrite.default.title()
      );
      const eventbriteBlock = new _eventbrite.default(blockId, page, eventId);
      await eventbriteBlock.addEmbed();
    }
  );
  await (0, _reporter.testStep)(
    "Can publish a post with a Eventbrite block",
    async () => {
      await blockEditor.selectPostTitle();
      await blockEditor.publishPost();
      await blockEditor.viewPost();
    }
  );
  await (0, _reporter.testStep)(
    "Can assert that Eventbrite block is rendered",
    async () => {
      const frontend = await _postFrontend.default.init(page);

      expect(
        await frontend.isRenderedBlockPresent(_eventbrite.default, {
          eventId,
        })
      ).toBeTruthy();
    }
  );
};
